%% Supervisor-Worker 多 Agent 编排

flowchart TB
  CTX[案件上下文\nCaseWorkContext]
  SUP((Supervisor\n调度智能体))

  CTX --> SUP

  SUP --> AG1[GuidanceAgent\n办事资源]
  SUP --> AG2[EvidenceAgent\nOCR·证据链]
  SUP --> AG3[ResearchAgent\n深度研究]
  SUP --> AG4[DocgenAgent\n文书推荐生成]
  SUP --> AG5[RecordsAgent\n材料包·记录]

  AG1 & AG2 & AG3 & AG4 & AG5 --> EVAL[evaluate_all_agents]
  EVAL --> PICK[_pick_next_proposal]
  PICK --> NEXT[GET /cases/id/agent/next-step]
